"title": "8459: perseverance",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8459",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Enduring in a course of action or belief. In its negative sense, it can mean being stubborn; in its positive sense, it means continuing commitment to the gospel of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Human perseverance in sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:41\">2KI 17:41</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:5\">ISA 1:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:32\">ROM 1:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:1-Exod9:3\">EXO 9:1–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:19\">DEU 29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:17\">JDG 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:11\">2KI 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:10\">DAN 12:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's perseverance in calling Israel to obedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30-Neh9:31\">NEH 9:30–9:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:14\">EXO 32:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:6\">1KI 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:13\">JER 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:10\">JON 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's perseverance with those who would not believe</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:3\">HEB 12:1–12:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:17\">MAT 17:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:19\">MRK 9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:5\">2TH 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Christians' perseverance in faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:6-Col2:7\">COL 2:6–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10-Col1:12\">COL 1:10–1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:12-Matt24:13\">MAT 24:12–24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:22\">MAT 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4-John15:10\">JHN 15:4–15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:22\">ROM 11:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:8\">1CO 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:15\">2CO 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12\">PHP 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:23\">COL 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:4\">2TH 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:1\">HEB 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:36-Heb10:38\">HEB 10:36–10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Perseverance in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:1-Luke18:8\">LUK 18:1–18:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:5-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:5–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:17\">1TH 5:17</a></p>\n<h2>Perseverance arises from suffering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3\">ROM 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:6\">2CO 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2TH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10-2Tim3:11\">2TI 3:10–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:3\">JAS 1:2–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:2-Rev2:3\">REV 2:2–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a></p>\n<h2>Perseverance builds and demonstrates Christian character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:4\">ROM 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:7\">1CO 13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:12\">2CO 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:4\">JAS 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:8\">2PE 1:5–1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Encouragements for Christians to persevere</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:23\">ACT 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:43\">ACT 13:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:13\">2TI 1:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:1\">HEB 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:14\">HEB 4:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:11\">REV 3:11</a></p>",
